---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: "Software picks, comparisons, and category explainers for solo founders and 5–50 person teams—written to surface the hidden issues."
---

<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero__eyebrow">Small teams · real constraints</p>
  <h1 class="hero__title">Buy software with your eyes open.</h1>
  <p class="hero__lede">
    Long-form reviews, tight roundups, and A-vs-B comparisons focused on what vendor homepages smooth over: pricing cliffs, admin overhead,
    edge-case bugs, and the “sounds cheap until you scale” traps.
  </p>
</section>

<ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li class="post-card">
      <div class="post-card__meta">
        <span class="post-card__type">{{ post.data.type | contentTypeLabel }}</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
      </div>
      <h2 class="post-card__title">
        <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      {% if post.data.description %}
        <p class="post-card__dek">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
